It had equal parts mystery, ethical debates, excellent, intelligent writing, and more questions than answers. Season 3 is trying to introduce the real world when it is only going to damage the show's potential. Staying within the parks is what made this show special. Shame on these showrunners and their horrible decisions, such as bringing on Aaron Paul. *Shudders* He's a stupid, low intellect pothead.
